    "4fc05ee5-1c30-4863-b88f-81cb6fa7c41a": {
      "type": "icons-with-content",
      "blocks": {
        "template--21507361800487__4fc05ee5-1c30-4863-b88f-81cb6fa7c41a-icon-1": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "auto_stories",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "title": "Born in Formula 1",
            "text": "<p>Carbon fiber entered motorsport in 1981 when McLaren built the first F1 carbon chassis. It changed racing forever. Now it's on your wrist.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "template--21507361800487__4fc05ee5-1c30-4863-b88f-81cb6fa7c41a-icon-2": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "build",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "title": "Stronger. Lighter. Rarer.",
            "text": "<p>5x stronger than steel. 40% lighter than titanium. Each forged carbon piece has a unique pattern — no two watches are identical.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "template--21507361800487__4fc05ee5-1c30-4863-b88f-81cb6fa7c41a-icon-3": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "military_tech",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "title": "The Prestige Standard",
            "text": "<p>Every watch hand-inspected against strict criteria for movement quality, finishing, and case integrity before it ships.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "template--21507361800487__4fc05ee5-1c30-4863-b88f-81cb6fa7c41a-heading-1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why Carbon Fiber Changes Everything",
            "title_highlight_color": "#c9a84c",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "template--21507361800487__4fc05ee5-1c30-4863-b88f-81cb6fa7c41a-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Steel is the default. Titanium is the upgrade. Carbon fiber is the obsession.<\/p><p>Forged carbon fiber was developed for one purpose: maximum strength at minimum weight in environments where failure is not an option — Formula 1 cars, fighter jets, space-grade equipment. It is not a cosmetic choice. It is an engineering choice.<\/p><p>At Prestige, we apply that same obsession to watchmaking. Every Luxury Forged Carbon Fiber Watch is built around a case compressed under 500 tons of pressure, finished by hand, paired with a Swiss automatic movement trusted by serious collectors worldwide.<\/p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "template--21507361800487__4fc05ee5-1c30-4863-b88f-81cb6fa7c41a-button-1": {
          "type": "button",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Claim Your Carbon Watch — Save $400 Today",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style_secondary": false
          }
        }
      },
